\nw[\N[21]]Do you have any idea what might have caused Prae

unwell.

strange since I heard the conversation at the
Water Temple.
\nw[\N[21]]Huh, what do you mean?
\nw[Louis]Don't you seriously understand?

\nw[\N[21]]What's with the suspense? Even if you say we
talked at the Water Temple, we were just
communicating, right?

\nw[\N[21]]The contract was supposed to allow her to use it

smaller... Could it be that it was a lie?

owner was communicating. It's probably not a
problem.

\nw[\N[21]]I see... Is there anything else that comes to
mind...
\nw[\N[21]]I can't think of anything...

\nw[Louis]The captain drifted to an island with the Water
Temple while still unconscious, right? They were
thrown off the ship at a distance of about half a
day to the island. And they were with the Blue
Songstress.

\nw[Louis]Do you really think something like that could
happen without any consequences?
\nw[\N[21]]......!? No... I thought it was just good luck...

\nw[\N[21]]Now that you mention it... it's definitely a
probability that can only be described as a
miracle...

constantly confirm the captain's whereabouts and
be magically connected, they might even be able to
guide them.

\nw[Louis]Of course, there is only one person like that,
right?
\nw[\N[21]]......Could it be... I've been saved again...?

\nw[Louis]Judging from the evidence, there is no doubt,
right? If the captain was saved by chance, there
would be no reason for the owner to become unwell.

\nw[\N[21]]...Are you saying that you collapsed to save
me...?
\nw[\N[21]]...I'm always being saved by that person...

Several days later, Prae was discharged from the
hospital. It wasn't because her condition had
improved, but rather because her condition
couldn't be treated in the first place.

She is probably the only demon from the Demon
World in this country, and it seems that her body
structure is quite unique. Moreover, since she has
become a child, she says she doesn't really
understand it well.

It seems like she's in the same condition as
before from what I can see, but I think she might
be pushing herself too hard in reality.
